Scopronok walked out of his lab. "Megatron, We have about 3 or 4 
people looking for QuickStrike, and we had thoose 4, that quit our 
group." Scopornok walked into single file of the line. "May I make a 
suggestion. We ally ourselves with one of the 4 major powers. The 4 
powers being, alliance, maximals, Rampage Predacon, and The 
newcommers. With us allied with 1 of these we can over power the 
enemy, and get more bots, that we reprogram."
